ille]]\n| [[Kentucky]]<br>[[Indiana]]\n|[[File:Louisville skyline night.jpg|130px]]\n| align=right | 1,395,634\n| align=right | 1,602,456\n| align=right |   206,822\n| align=right | 14.8\n|-\n| align=right | 16\n| [[Grand Rapids metropolitan area|Grand Rapids]]\n| [[Michigan]]\n|[[File:Grdowntown.jpg|130px]]\n| align=right | 1,327,366\n| align=right | 1,530,000\n| align=right |   202,634\n| align=right | 15.3\n|-\n| align=right | 17\n| [[Buffalo \u2013 Niagara Falls metropolitan area|Buffalo]]\n| [[New York (state)|New York]]\n|[[File:BuffaloSkyline.jpg|130px]]\n| align=right | 1,203,493\n| align=right | 1,251,633\n| align=right | 48,140\n| align=right | 6\n|-\n| align=right | 18\n| [[Rochester, New York metropolitan area|Rochester]]\n| [[New York (state)|New York]]\n|[[File:Skyline Rochester, NY.jpg|130px]]\n| align=right | 1,149,653\n| align=right | 1,133,558\n| align=right | -16,095\n| align=right | -1.4\n|-\n| align=right | 19\n| [[Dayton metropolitan area|Dayton]]\n| [[Ohio]]\n|[[File:Dayton Skyline.jpg|130px]]\n| align=right | 1,066,261\n| align=right | 1,066,261\n| align=right |         0\n| align=right | 0\n|-\n| align=right | 20\n| [[Hamilton, Ontario|Hamilton]]\n| [[Ontario]]\n|[[File:HamiltonOntarioSkylineC.JPG|130px]]\n| align=right | 740,200\n| align=right | 954,858\n| align=right | 214,658\n| align=right | 29.1\n|-\n| align=right | 21\n| [[South Bend, IN|South Bend-Mishawaka-Elkhart]]\n| [[Indiana]]<br>[[Michigan]]\n|[[File:City of South Bend, downtown skyline.jpg|130px]]\n| align=right | 720,647\n| align=right | NA\n| align=right | NA\n| align=right | NA\n|-\n| align=right | 22\n| [[Toledo, Ohio metropolitan area|Toledo]]\n| [[Ohio]]<br>[[Michigan]]\n| [[File:Skyline of Toledo, Ohio.jpg|130px]]\n| align=right | 672,220\n| align=right | 672,220\n| align=right | 0\n| align=right | 0\n|-\n| align=right | 23\n| [[Madison, Wisconsin metropolitan area|Madison]]\n| [[Wisconsin]]\n|[[File:Madisonwisconsin20060813p001.jpg|130px]]\n| align=right | 628,947\n| al